":14337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T03:43:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>柬蒲寨暹粒機場d海關貪得眾勁</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我去過 <br />\n一蚊都冇比過 而且仲好快比我入境出境"},{"pid":"a16aec477c638718ce3013140d96f492da1bdf42","tid":32344,"uid":11161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T03:47:13.000Z","msg":"kix t2"},{"pid":"0382f3af90bbc53f1b2c5bc0b494195c8ea82c48","tid":32344,"uid":36272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T03:47:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>台中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n三四年前內陸同國際線同一個大樓 又舊又逼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家起多個航廈專比國際線好好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBTW有時係起跑道會有戰機睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4756500a1586029f65e2dc9002f3d483324b8763","tid":32344,"uid":54359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T03:54:01.000Z","msg":"所有距離市中心over 30mins車程就係廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n除左羽田同福岡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6513e48057f3d278d99c6a37e8854c4a5fbbf3d7","tid":32344,"uid":35331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T03:58:13.000Z","msg":"孟加拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個機場細過港外線碼頭<br />\nD人又唔識排隊 亂咁企+打尖<br />\n機場出面d人會話幫你手推行理然後收tips <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n試過入面突然話要收機場稅～50hkd到<br />\n我又洗曬d錢（孟加拉紙香港冇人收<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n咁話美金/港紙得唔得？<br />\n佢話收美金不過冇得找(我得張100老美<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n之後好彩我搵到有張馬來西亞紙換返夠數先走得<br />\n<br />\n本身幾ok lee個地方<br />\n臨走lee一鑊真係搞到我唔會再去"},{"pid":"aa09a23d6fcb804d1a92d18b852e200a0a89e5e1","tid":32344,"uid":12070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T04:01:39.000Z","msg":"Ex"},{"pid":"ab0648b2017d1df5e516a14c504245844acc0e56","tid":32344,"uid":57543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T04:13:31.000Z","msg":"浦東<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 燈又唔開，廁所又勁污糟"},{"pid":"2d3eda9602ebd2b4cd3f187eafa5984f0d06d86d","tid":32344,"uid":57543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T04:14:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Chicago O'hare</blockquote><br />\n次次都預夠三個鐘時間轉機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d5b5ff465bc2735e63462807d5dd7af6448f66c","tid":32344,"uid":23656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T04:17:50.000Z","msg":"布吉<br />\n<br />\n啲工作人員收錢比啲支那人用特快通道<br />\n仲係到用支那話大叫 &quot;收費特快通道&quot;"},{"pid":"fd9e90536e41b7dd8266dd00af33a8ff10444015","tid":32344,"uid":34891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T04:19:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>柬蒲寨暹粒機場d海關貪得眾勁</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nagger<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我冇俾錢d海關，佢地扣住我本passport勁耐，搞一大輪野先入到境"},{"pid":"a3e742e86ba058989b27dfb1b1f78ccbcd3e020d","tid":32344,"uid":39195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T04:20:22.000Z","msg":"埃及 luxor, 沙，全部都係沙 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/search?q=egypt+luxor+airport&amp;prmd=imnv&amp;source=lnms&amp;tbm=isch&amp;sa=X&amp;ved=0ahUKEwiqpJrko-vQAhUCI5QKHf7DAKAQ_AUIBygB&amp;biw=360&amp;bih=560#imgrc=X97SNOUuhbjsfM%3A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Fsearch%3Fq%3Degypt%2Bluxor%2Bairport%26prmd%3Dimnv%26source%3Dlnms%26tbm%3Disch%26sa%3