似比班友點到趕到仆街<br />\n而且Newark咁大個城市 點解個機場咁爛咁舊<br />\n下次情願都係經西岸入返呢再轉 真係貼錢買難受<br />\n住Jersey個位 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個人覺得JFK好過EWR <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  (小小)"},{"pid":"2c2eb4671dfc9e8495d5a73a63326b6067f3f628","tid":32344,"uid":6520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T13:42:57.000Z","msg":"台中？ 上次去無乜問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n沖繩坐HX 拎pass果陣條龍長到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  又唔set好啲<br />\n<br />\n搞到成條長人鏈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"755391937f242a3344deca83de0851a45efc3a27","tid":32344,"uid":5637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T13:50:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>barcelona. 又垃圾又亂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nAgger ,真係垃撚圾，啲扶手電梯全部裝假狗，排隊又亂到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c5904543bf34dfa63e804c5d5b94271d23c8eab","tid":32344,"uid":2601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T14:01:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>布吉<br />\n<br />\n啲工作人員收錢比啲支那人用特快通道<br />\n仲係到用支那話大叫 &quot;收費特快通道&quot;</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實啲人都係比10蚊 20蚊人仔就可以行特快<br />\n<br />\n我地4條友真係好唔憤氣 點解要比你賺 跟住排普通果條隊 排左個個2個鐘 不過果陣凌晨機 book 左架車都要天光先到 慢慢磨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16baa05cbd995f3c236fa46d71073f996a81f273","tid":32344,"uid":12518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T14:02:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"219712b4b0c6d88f0771a48feafc358ec7f5bd76","tid":32344,"uid":11805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T14:05:02.000Z","msg":"Heathrow<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4b721d8547c817e7d8c11395008948b1d2a807b","tid":32344,"uid":33664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T14:10:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講開印尼 啲貪污真係痴鳩線&hellip; 好多&ldquo;修路&rdquo; 咁就有人黎指揮交通 屌個啲人夠膽死收完你錢先俾你過<br />\n同埋啲古跡公園啲staff會叫外國人去簽名 好似留念咁 點知之後就問你攞錢<br />\n<br />\n不過印尼啲人幾好 民風純樸 影到好多相 我會再去 但係去呢啲落後地方真係要小心啲官員</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n比過路費真係痴線 前後比過唔少次<br />\n一見有制服佬揮幾揮就好拎定錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有扮傷殘嘅人9彈結他 局住你比錢佢"},{"pid":"887ee21e7b25e5c7ef2562b8d306ba5a15bd8a9a","tid":32344,"uid":2603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T14:29:45.000Z","msg":"至尊 龍濤閣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b539de93fa70c406b7ccd15dd52a4e60fc977d8b","tid":32344,"uid":50144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T14:34:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>JFK EWR<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n打死都唔會再用EWR <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nJFK大劑好多......<br />\n<br />\nbtw我推薦巴拿馬Tocumen<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 行李車要3蚊美金，同市區遠到冇譜之餘仲要冇公共交通工具<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3de6d5e773b88b9e49dbbee825974b904784d283","tid":32344,"uid":48473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T14:37:21.000Z","msg":"KL for廉航果個<br />\n機場食肆周圍勁多烏蠅 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9540525a7c4e376fc73ff4f151e49f84d24e31cf","tid":32344,"uid":14779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T16:50:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><bl